{
  "specVersion": "0.1",
  "domain": {
    "name": "support_triage",
    "description": "Customer-support triage & resolution (use case #1). A TriageAgent classifies an inbound ticket, retrieves the governing policy, and PROPOSES a resolution. Low-risk tier-1 proposals auto-execute; anything above the risk bar enters an OutSystems approval workflow (BPT) for a human to sign off before the write lands. Every action is audited. The bounded action space (reply | auto-resolve | escalate) + the human-at-the-write-step is what makes it ship, not just reason.",
    "entities": [
      {
        "name": "Customer",
        "context": "support",
        "naturalKey": "Email",
        "attributes": [
          {
            "name": "Email",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "Name",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "Tier",
            "dataType": "Text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "PolicyDoc",
        "context": "support",
        "naturalKey": "Code",
        "attributes": [
          {
            "name": "Code",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "Title",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "Category",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "Content",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "length": 2000
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "Ticket",
        "context": "support",
        "naturalKey": "TicketNo",
        "references": [
          "Customer"
        ],
        "attributes": [
          {
            "name": "TicketNo",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "Subject",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "Body",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "length": 2000
          },
          {
            "name": "Channel",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "Category",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "Priority",
            "dataType": "Integer"
          },
          {
            "name": "Status",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "ConfidenceScore",
            "dataType": "Integer"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "ResolutionAction",
        "context": "support",
        "references": [
          "Ticket"
        ],
        "attributes": [
          {
            "name": "ActionType",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true
          },
          {
            "name": "DraftBody",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "length": 2000
          },
          {
            "name": "RiskTier",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "Status",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "ApprovedBy",
            "dataType": "Text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "AuditEvent",
        "context": "support",
        "references": [
          "Ticket"
        ],
        "attributes": [
          {
            "name": "Description",
            "dataType": "Text",
            "mandatory": true,
            "length": 2000
          },
          {
            "name": "Actor",
            "dataType": "Text"
          },
          {
            "name": "At",
            "dataType": "DateTime"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "actors": [
      "customer",
      "support_agent",
      "admin"
    ],
    "capabilities": [
      {
        "name": "SubmitTicket",
        "actor": "customer",
        "reads": [
          "Customer"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "Ticket",
          "AuditEvent"
        ],
        "service": "SubmitTicket",
        "raisesEvent": "TicketSubmitted",
        "note": "Public intake \u2014 creates the ticket and kicks off triage."
      },
      {
        "name": "TriageTicket",
        "ai": "TriageAgent",
        "reads": [
          "Ticket",
          "PolicyDoc",
          "Customer"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "Ticket",
          "ResolutionAction",
          "AuditEvent"
        ],
        "service": "TriageTicket",
        "note": "THE AGENT. Grounds on Ticket + PolicyDoc (native retrieval tool), classifies (Category/Priority/Confidence), drafts a resolution, and PROPOSES a ResolutionAction (reply|auto_resolve|escalate) with a RiskTier. It never writes the customer-facing resolution directly \u2014 it proposes."
      },
      {
        "name": "ResolveTicket",
        "actor": "support_agent",
        "reads": [
          "Ticket",
          "ResolutionAction"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "Ticket",
          "ResolutionAction",
          "AuditEvent"
        ],
        "service": "ResolveTicket",
        "note": "The bounded WRITE to the system of record: mark the ResolutionAction executed + the Ticket resolved, audited. Called by the workflow after approval (or auto for low-risk)."
      },
      {
        "name": "EscalateTicket",
        "actor": "support_agent",
        "reads": [
          "Ticket"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "Ticket",
          "AuditEvent"
        ],
        "service": "EscalateTicket",
        "note": "The other bounded write: route to a human queue, audited."
      },
      {
        "name": "ResolutionWorkflow",
        "orchestrates": true,
        "triggerEvent": "TicketSubmitted",
        "steps": [
          {
            "name": "Triage",
            "ai": "TriageAgent",
            "reads": [
              "Ticket",
              "PolicyDoc"
            ],
            "writes": [
              "ResolutionAction"
            ]
          },
          {
            "name": "Approve",
            "callsService": "ResolveTicket"
          }
        ],
        "note": "HITL via OutSystems BPT: on TicketSubmitted the workflow runs the TriageAgent to produce a proposed ResolutionAction; low RiskTier auto-calls ResolveTicket, higher RiskTier holds at a Human Approval activity until a support_agent approves, THEN calls ResolveTicket/EscalateTicket. The approval + audit is native workflow, not custom code."
      },
      {
        "name": "MyQueue",
        "actor": "support_agent",
        "reads": [
          "Ticket",
          "ResolutionAction",
          "Customer"
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "ApprovalInbox",
        "actor": "support_agent",
        "reads": [
          "ResolutionAction",
          "Ticket"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "ResolutionAction",
          "AuditEvent"
        ],
        "service": "ApproveResolution",
        "note": "Where a human approves/rejects a held high-risk proposal \u2014 the write-step sign-off."
      },
      {
        "name": "ManagePolicies",
        "actor": "admin",
        "reads": [
          "PolicyDoc"
        ],
        "writes": [
          "PolicyDoc"
        ],
        "service": "SavePolicy",
        "note": "Admin maintains the policy corpus the agent grounds on."
      },
      {
        "name": "AuditTrail",
        "actor": "admin",
        "reads": [
          "AuditEvent",
          "Ticket"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "integrations": [
      {
        "name": "KnowledgeBase",
        "kind": "consume",
        "purpose": "optional external policy source (SharePoint-style REST) the TriageAgent can retrieve from as a tool",
        "stub": true
      },
      {
        "name": "Notify",
        "kind": "consume",
        "purpose": "customer/agent notifications on resolution or escalation",
        "stub": true
      }
    ],
    "libraries": [
      "SupportDesignSystem"
    ]
  }
}
